00:43:08,987 --> 00:43:11,347
Floods, sandbars, fallen logs--

807
00:43:11,707 --> 00:43:13,987
It was all a riverboat pilot could do was to

808
00:43:14,027 --> 00:43:17,107
know his little piece of the puzzle.

