820
00:43:56,588 --> 00:44:00,187
OK, now, now, it ap-appears
we're losing reception here.

821
00:44:01,388 --> 00:44:03,549
OK, we've--we've
lost picture now.

822
00:44:03,628 --> 00:44:05,708
But we will stay on the air.

823
00:44:05,789 --> 00:44:08,669
We'll stay with you
through all of this.

824
00:44:14,029 --> 00:44:15,389
<i>Dap is in descent.</i>

825
00:44:15,468 --> 00:44:16,988
<i>Tanner, Over intercom: Roger, descent.</i>

826
00:44:21,748 --> 00:44:23,028
[Alarm Beeping]

827
00:44:23,628 --> 00:44:24,988
Oh, my God.

828
00:44:24,988 --> 00:44:27,428
Baker: Look at these.
