829
00:44:27,508 --> 00:44:28,508
Yeah, I know.

830
00:44:28,587 --> 00:44:30,227
I see.

831
00:44:42,348 --> 00:44:44,749
Jesus Christ.

832
00:44:46,188 --> 00:44:47,148
[Beeping]

