00:48:23,593 --> 00:48:24,913
<i>Tanner: Mark, what's your mole 4 readout?</i>

866
00:48:24,993 --> 00:48:27,473
<i>Simon: Mole 4 running true at 75 feet.</i>

867
00:48:27,553 --> 00:48:30,353
[Beeping]

