00:48:33,953 --> 00:48:35,033
It's stuck.

871
00:48:35,153 --> 00:48:36,113
Try backing it up.

872
00:48:36,513 --> 00:48:37,233
<i>Baker: What's your depth?</i>

873
00:48:37,553 --> 00:48:38,593
75 feet.

