00:52:51,717 --> 00:52:54,118
He's got escape velocity.
1 ,000 feet and climbing.

931
00:52:55,238 --> 00:52:57,357
Aah!

932
00:52:57,477 --> 00:53:00,237
Mark, Mikhail, get
the hell out of there!

