00:54:14,599 --> 00:54:16,079
If we go back for Gus,
we all die.

951
00:54:16,199 --> 00:54:18,279
We can't just
leave him in space!

952
00:54:19,279 --> 00:54:22,839
Sit down, Mick.  Sit down.
It's OK

