00:54:37,160 --> 00:54:40,359
<i>But sadly, Gus Partenza has been lost.</i>

955
00:54:40,520 --> 00:54:43,799
Gus Partenza, a native of
Harrisburg, Pennsylvania,

956
00:54:43,880 --> 00:54:46,841
and graduate of Carnegie-Mellon University,

