00:54:48,641 --> 00:54:53,400
shortly after completing his
medical training at Duke University.

959
00:54:53,481 --> 00:54:56,520
Dr Partenza was selected
specifically for this mission,

960
00:54:56,600 --> 00:54:59,200
not only for his
medical expertise,

961
00:54:59,320 --> 00:55:03,921
but also for his dedication to the
advancement of space technology.

962
00:55:06,520 --> 00:55:07,640
Yeah.

963
00:55:17,201 --> 00:55:20,840
<i>With the loss of Dr Gus Partenza
and with Oren Monash injured,</i>

