00:58:32,244 --> 00:58:34,164
<i>the other, a mile and a half.</i>

997
00:58:34,244 --> 00:58:37,964
<i>Both are still on a path
towards Earth.</i>

998
00:58:38,044 --> 00:58:40,164
<i>We've lost communication with
